title: Carole Baskin Finally Comes On The Show + Raymundo Makes Decision On Wedding Ring + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Shaq’s House
itunes:title: Carole Baskin Finally Comes On The Show + Raymundo Makes Decision On Wedding Ring + Lunchbox Tries To Buy Shaq’s House
description:
After months of trying to get her to come on the show, Carole Baskin from Netflix's 'Tiger King' and ABC's 'Dancing With The Stars' finally joins us for an interview. Raymundo makes a decision on his new wedding ring. Amy tells us what her therapist has recommended for her to help deal with stress. Plus, Lunchbox does a prank call where he tries to buy Shaq’s multi-million dollar house!
